{
  "id": "adv_event_2406_02_02",
  "title": "サニピ_大感謝.mov",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_chs-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "……ここに立てばいいんだよね？\nあれ……もう撮ってる……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I’m supposed to stand here‚ right?\nHuh… You’re already filming…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 6.3703175545,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_chs-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "うん……大丈夫。録画はもう、始まってる！\nいつでも、喋っていいよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah… It’s fine. Recording has already started!\nYou can start talking anytime.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.5666666667,
      "endTime": 12.355555407299999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_chs-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、こんに千紗！\nサニーピースの、白石千紗です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚ konnichi-Chisa!\nI’m Chisa Shiraishi from Sunny Peace!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.233334605,
      "endTime": 19.2000011127,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_chs-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "以前考えた挨拶を使ってみました。えへへ\n私の感謝の気持ちを、この動画に込めたいと思います",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I tried using the greeting I thought of before. Ehehe.\nI want to put my feelings of gratitude into this video!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.5666673025,
      "endTime": 29.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_chs-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "ええと……改めて伝えたいこと、沢山あるんです\nその中でも、ずっと忘れられないことがあって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Um… There are so many things I want to tell you again.\nAmong them‚ there’s something I can never forget.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.3000010174,
      "endTime": 39.2162367504,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_chs-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "星見まつりのこと、覚えてますか？　来れなくなった\nお父さんのかわりに一緒に屋台を回ってくれましたよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Do you remember the Hoshimi Festival? You went around the stalls with me\nin place of my father who couldn’t make it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.4000010174,
      "endTime": 49.4136974972,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_chs-chs006.m4a",
      "text": "本当はしょんぼりしてたので、とっても嬉しかったです\nありがとうございました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was actually feeling down‚ so I was really happy.\nThank you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.6000010174,
      "endTime": 56.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_chs-chs007.m4a",
      "text": "あの時、{user}さんの後ろを歩いてて\n凄く安心したんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "At that time‚ while walking behind {user}-san‚\nI felt really safe.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.7666689556,
      "endTime": 63.0090274494,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_chs-chs008.m4a",
      "text": "まるで本当のお父さんみたいで……\n私にとって、とても素敵な思い出になりました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It was like you were my real dad…\nIt became a very precious memory for me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.3333374024,
      "endTime": 71.8585981369,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_chs-chs009.m4a",
      "text": "これからも、温かく見守ってくれると嬉しいです\n本当に、いつもありがとう。お父さん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’d be happy if you continue to watch over me warmly from now on.\nThank you so much‚ Dad.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.0666707357,
      "endTime": 80.4119769415,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_chs-chs010.m4a",
      "text": "……えっ、あっ！　す、すすすみません！\n間違えました！　{user}さん、です！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Eh‚ ah! I-I’m so sorry!\nI made a mistake! It’s {user}-san!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.8000010173,
      "endTime": 87.49059073139999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_chs-chs011.m4a",
      "text": "うう……雫ちゃん、最後はカットで……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Uuu… Shizuku-chan‚ please cut the last part…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.7000010173,
      "endTime": 91.6404545943,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_szk-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、やっほー\nサニーピースの、兵藤雫です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚ hello!\nI’m Shizuku Hyodo from Sunny Peace.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.9404561202,
      "endTime": 99.38233806299999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_szk-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "この動画は、星見プロのみんなで、お送りしています\n超超、お宝映像になると思う……期待してて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This video is brought to you by everyone at Hoshimi Pro.\nIt’ll be a super‚ super precious video… Look forward to it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.5934493224,
      "endTime": 109.9127221267,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_szk-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん……いつも、好きなお仕事を\n取ってきてくれてありがとう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san… Thank you for always bringing\nme jobs that I like.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.1267815113,
      "endTime": 117.1899336338,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_szk-szk004.m4a",
      "text": "最近、釣り関係のお仕事が沢山で、凄く楽しい\nなるべく立ち会ってくれてるのも……嬉しい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Lately‚ there have been a lot of jobs related to fishing‚ which is really fun.\nAnd I’m also happy that… you’re there with me as much as possible.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.393448178,
      "endTime": 127.6558190505,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_szk-szk005.m4a",
      "text": "アングラークイーンになれたのも\n{user}さんのおかげ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was able to become Angler Queen\nthanks to {user}-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.8601049265,
      "endTime": 131.9647325834,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_szk-szk006.m4a",
      "text": "それにあの時は、風邪の看病もしてくれた\n{user}さんは、命の恩人",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And back then‚ you took care of me when I had a cold‚\nyou’re my lifesaver.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.1601067066,
      "endTime": 139.47378945350002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_szk-szk007.m4a",
      "text": "……ハッ！　思い返してみると、それ以外にも\nまだまだ感謝したいことが一杯ある……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Huh! When I think back on it‚ besides that‚\nthere are still so many things I want to thank you for…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.7267779509,
      "endTime": 147.27482768689998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_szk-szk008.m4a",
      "text": "まだアイドルでもない、ただの兵藤雫だった私のことを\n見つけてくれたし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You found me when I was just Shizuku Hyodo‚\nnot even an idol yet.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.4601112842,
      "endTime": 153.81981654159998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_szk-szk009.m4a",
      "text": "アイドルになってからも、うまく喋れない私のことを\n沢山フォローしてくれて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And even after I became an idol‚\nyou helped me out a lot.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.0267779509,
      "endTime": 160.109453694,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_szk-szk010.m4a",
      "text": "この間の夏祭りの時も、浴衣を、そのっ……\nほ、他にもっ――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And at the summer festival a while ago‚ the yukata… um…\nA-and… other things――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 160.2934446176,
      "endTime": 166.6310405572,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_szk-szk011.m4a",
      "text": "え？　尺が延びてる？　それはまずい。えっと\nと、とにかく、私の大感謝は、以上です……！　ぶい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? It’s getting long? That’s bad. Um‚\na-anyway‚ this concludes my huge thanks…! V.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 166.7601163705,
      "endTime": 176.6267953713,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_skr-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "えへへ、{user}さん\nお疲れ様です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ehehe‚ {user}-san!\nGood work.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 178.9268046578,
      "endTime": 183.14106766790002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_skr-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "えーっとですね、デビューする前、私が歯磨き粉を\n買いに行く途中に偶然会って話したのを覚えてますか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Um‚ do you remember when we met by chance\nand talked on the way to buy toothpaste before my debut?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 183.3268046578,
      "endTime": 192.9621785362,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_skr-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "あの時、私「{user}さんを見た時に\n心臓がドキンといった」って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Back then‚ I told you‚ “When I saw {user}-san‚\nmy heart skipped a beat.”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 193.1601379911,
      "endTime": 200.8922692815,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_skr-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "「あ、この人だ」と思ったって伝えたんですよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I said‚ “Ah‚ this is the one!”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 201.0934713245,
      "endTime": 206.1753536106,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_skr-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっとした立ち話だったけど\n私にとっては、すっごく思い出深くて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even though it was just a brief conversation‚\nit was a really memorable moment for me…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 206.3601379911,
      "endTime": 212.5769389669,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
